						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the Āñjanēya temple outside the village.</p>						

						<p>Damaged and fragmentary. Seems to record a gift of land to [Bhō]laśakti-Paṇḍita for the <hi rend="italic">satram</hi> of the god Bhōgēśvara. In characters of about the 13th century A.D.</p>						

